title: WWI effect on culture and soc. between wars

content.question: Directions: The suggested writing time for this question is 35 minutes. Make sure that you are best prepared to answer the question thoroughly in the time permitted. You should spend 5 minutes organizing or outlining your essay. In writing your essays, use specific examples to support your answer. If time permits when you finish writing, check your work.Analyze the impact of the First World War on European culture and society in the interwar period (1919-1939).
